 the analysis\nduring the flaring state of the source one can say that the emissions most\nlikely originate from the jet rather than the accretion disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 May 2022 16:40:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-20"}
