trained (n=5,6) to a softer system\n(n=10,12) was revealed with increasing alkyl chain length. A counterbalance of\ntwo competing effects of a polyethylene like behavior of the alkyl chains in\nthe intercolumnar domains and self-organized confinement is discussed in the\ncontext of a hindered glass transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 May 2022 19:31:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-06"}
